{"tid":890671,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"五毛狗玩撚夠未?","createTime":"2018-11-05T13:14:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-13T09:55:37.000Z","uid":48234,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"83d5892e3f1341f7822801709459a3f620c5f63c","tid":890671,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T13:14:24.000Z","msg":"屌你老母臭閪,五毛狗不停製造混亂<br />\n不過啲五毛狗全部都未出過嚟,未試過街頭抗爭<br />\n蔣狗,屌你老母,你俾人起撚晒底,地址都起撚埋,你有冇出過嚟抗爭係人都知<br />\n關愛座hunter就出過嚟啦,你呢?去撚咗邊?<br />\n蔣狗,你敢唔敢喺上街抗爭?<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">你連參加遊行示威都仲未敢呀,五毛狗</span></span>"},{"pid":"5b314ee0be86fd98295a6d82b573074c86f1fc4b","tid":890671,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T13:17:12.000Z","msg":"咁五毛黎架嘛⋯⋯要五毛參加港獨遊行示威，你想逼死五毛咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我係咪認真左<br />\n<br />\n我好似認真左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11e3c2cf0b66a12a480ea8d0e8e5122b7d9f9ed7","tid":890671,"uid":27451,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T13:17:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/05/211753_265c285eb063c565731c1b87bec0b1a1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F05%2F211753_265c285eb063c565731c1b87bec0b1a1.png&h=77016d51&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/05/211754_f8290d708b0d724b0e94e8e6055c7464.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F05%2F211754_f8290d708b0d724b0e94e8e6055c7464.png&h=ec0a3862&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa4deb519fc5e71b839ea4720650dcb485d583e9","tid":890671,"uid":2436,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T13:19:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9a9431d3e92c653744d3c25990b3e4d852e8fd53","tid":890671,"uid":2436,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"reply